author: cms-l1t-offline
body:
This brings L1T up to date with l1t-tsg-v6-cand, for everything except L1TNtuples (which will have a separate PR to reduce the size)

It depends on external https://github.com/cms-data/L1Trigger-L1TCalorimeter/pull/11
but for now the data files are included locally for testing.  (They'll be removed when external is in an IB).

The 80x request is #14362.
title: Update L1T to l1t-tsg-v6-cand (81x)
